OpenJDK @OPENJDK_VERSION@ for @TARGET_TRIPLE@

This prefix was built by develop_suit packages/openjdk.

OpenJDK target: @OPENJDK_TARGET_TRIPLE@
Maven version: @MAVEN_VERSION@
LLVM toolchain: @LLVM_VERSION@

Layout:

- jdk/: JDK image
- maven/: Apache Maven
- bin/java -> ../jdk/bin/java
- bin/javac -> ../jdk/bin/javac when the image includes jdk.compiler
- bin/mvn -> ../maven/bin/mvn

x86_64 and aarch64 Linux are packaged from Azul Zulu prebuilt JDK archives.
x86_64 MinGW/Windows is packaged from the Azul Zulu Windows x64 archive.
riscv64 and loongarch64 Linux are intended to be built from OpenJDK source with
a build-host Boot JDK. Source-built riscv64/loongarch64 packages are
service-runtime images without java.desktop/AWT.
